well hello.

i think i'm gonna move to Canada... so i can get married... i just moved in to an apartment with Sarah, my girlfriend. I'm REALLY happy about that. I'm having a great day, and week. I've been really busy, moving and all. I probably won't be writing on here for awhile... because i'm finishing up. Oops i have to go.. back to bed.. (smiles evily)
i died... lol. how is everyone? i'm great, but i gotta go!

nobody loves me... (cries)...lol anyways, how is everyone whose reading this? I'm having a great day! My girlfriend and I are going to see Resident Evil 2 on Saturday!!! YAY! I love her sooo much... ok, i gotta go now... see ya all

Vote Nicole!!
~Nici

*sigh* why do people fight pointless battles?... that annoys me to the greatest... or something like that...oh god, i'm starting to write like Andrea... (refers to the *sigh* above) well gotta go all my friends...
hello to all this is my NEW journal!!! cuz a friend didn't want her other friends to know her dirty secrets...
